Package org.locationtech.jts.jump.util.commandline

Class OptionSpec

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.locationtech.jts.jump.util.commandline.OptionSpec
  • public class OptionSpec
extends Object
    Specifes the syntax for a single option on a command line. ToDo: 
     - add syntax pattern parsing
      Syntax patterns are similar to Java type signatures
  F - float
  I - int
  L - long
  S - string
  B - boolean
  + - one or more
 eg:  "FIS+" takes a double, int, and one or more Strings
